Detailed Description

A netlist base class. This class owns its cells, nets and pins.

unsigned int NetlistBase::SOEDCost ( const std::vector< unsigned char > &  part,
unsigned int  numOfPartitions 
) const
Returns:
the cut cost in Sum-Of-External-Degrees (SOED) metric. The external degree of a partition is defined as the number of hyperedges, that are incident but not fully inside the partition. Take O(m) time.
the cut cost of partitions in Sum-Of-External-Degrees (SOED) metric. Note that the SOED cost is equal to the K-1 cost plus the HyperEdge cost.
